<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is a very funny book if you like historical fiction. Even if you are not a big fan of stories from long ago, you will like the characters because i<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â€¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is a very funny book if you like historical fiction. Even if you are not a big fan of stories from long ago, you will like the characters because it is a funny book. I have used this book as a novel study with students from grades 5 to 8 and they have all enjoyed it.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
