              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5684259-amy?shelf=2016">2016</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5684259-amy?shelf=2021">2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5684259-amy?shelf=read-aloud-john">read-aloud-john</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1518824246" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2761123851691782076">Wonderful story. Funny. Touching. Sophia (11 yo) and I both loved it.<br/><br/>Update: Just read this to my little boy (7 yo) as well. A classic. One of my all time favorite read alouds.</span>

          </span>
