<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8807415912249512662">Richard Peck was an American novelist known for his prolific contributions to modern young adult literature. He was awarded the Newbery Medal in 2001 for his novel <i>A Year Down Yonder</i>. For his cumulative contribution to young-adult literature, he received the Margaret A. Edwards Award from the American Library Association in 1990.<br/><br/></span>

</div>
